		title: "Orb of Rebirth"
		icon: {id: "mmorpg:currency/affix_random_mythic_reroll", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Forge an Orb of Rebirth in the Fusion Forge. Randomizes ALL affixes on an item to mythic-tier values simultaneously — the highest possible reroll across the entire affix system. Gate: Legendary Stone + Map Boss Drop + UHV Integrated Circuit."]
