		x: 14.0d
		y: 0.5d
		dependencies: ["0000000000040019"]
		title: "Sinistral Rebirth"
		icon: {id: "mmorpg:currency/prefix_reroll_all", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Forge a Sinistral Rebirth in the Fusion Forge. Rerolls WHICH prefixes are on an item — not the values of existing prefixes, but the actual affixes chosen. Unlike Western Ciphers (which keep the same prefixes and reroll numbers), this picks entirely new prefixes. Gate: Legendary Stone + Map Boss Drop + UHV Mainframe."]
		tasks: [{
