		description: ["Forge a Dextral Rebirth in the Fusion Forge. Rerolls WHICH suffixes are on an item — same mechanic as Sinistral Rebirth but for suffixes. Gate: Legendary Stone + Map Boss Drop + UHV Field Generator."]
